Pilot
Run an assistant-controlled autonomous work loop.

Usage:
$pilot start [--for <duration>] <goal>
$pilot status
$pilot pause
$pilot resume
$pilot wrap-up
$pilot stop

Options:
--for <duration>

Examples:
$pilot start --for 4h Improve benchmark accuracy end-to-end
$pilot wrap-up
